LEFT JOIN (

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Image], [p].[PodcastCategoryId], [p].[TeamMemberId], [p].[Title], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [p0].[Name], [t].[Id] AS [Id1], [t].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t].[FirstName], [t].[Image] AS [Image0], [t].[Information], [t].[LastName], [t].[SocialMedia]
    FROM [Podcasts] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [PodcastCategories] AS [p0] ON [p].[PodcastCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [TeamMembers] AS [t] ON [p].[TeamMemberId] = [t].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t0]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e].[Id], [e].[Audio], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Description], [e].[Image], [e].[PodcastId], [e].[Title], [l].[Id] AS [Id0], [l].[AppUserId], [l].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [l].[EpisodeId], [t2].[Id] AS [Id1], [t2].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t2].[EpisodeId] AS [EpisodeId0], [t2].[GuestId], [t2].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t2].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t2].[FirstName], [t2].[Image] AS [Image0], [t2].[Information], [t2].[LastName], [t2].[SocialMedia]
    FROM [Episodes] AS [e]
    LEFT JOIN [Likes] AS [l] ON [e].[Id] = [l].[EpisodeId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[CreatedDate], [e0].[EpisodeId], [e0].[GuestId], [g].[Id] AS [Id0], [g].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [g].[FirstName], [g].[Image], [g].[Information], [g].[LastName], [g].[SocialMedia]
        FROM [EpisodeGuests] AS [e0]
        INNER JOIN [Guests] AS [g] ON [e0].[GuestId] = [g].[Id]
    ) AS [t2] ON [e].[Id] = [t2].[EpisodeId]
) AS [t1] ON [t0].[Id] = [t1].[PodcastId]
ORDER BY [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id1]

FROM [Podcasts] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [PodcastCategories] AS [p0] ON [p].[PodcastCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [TeamMembers] AS [t] ON [p].[TeamMemberId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e].[Id], [e].[Audio], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Description], [e].[Image], [e].[PodcastId], [e].[Title], [l].[Id] AS [Id0], [l].[AppUserId], [l].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [l].[EpisodeId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id1], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[EpisodeId] AS [EpisodeId0], [t1].[GuestId], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[FirstName], [t1].[Image] AS [Image0], [t1].[Information], [t1].[LastName], [t1].[SocialMedia]
    FROM [Episodes] AS [e]
    LEFT JOIN [Likes] AS [l] ON [e].[Id] = [l].[EpisodeId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[CreatedDate], [e0].[EpisodeId], [e0].[GuestId], [g].[Id] AS [Id0], [g].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [g].[FirstName], [g].[Image], [g].[Information], [g].[LastName], [g].[SocialMedia]
        FROM [EpisodeGuests] AS [e0]
        INNER JOIN [Guests] AS [g] ON [e0].[GuestId] = [g].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [e].[Id] = [t1].[EpisodeId]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[PodcastId]
ORDER BY [p].[CreatedDate] DESC, [p].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Image], [p].[PodcastCategoryId], [p].[TeamMemberId], [p].[Title], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [p0].[Name], [t].[Id] AS [Id1], [t].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t].[FirstName], [t].[Image] AS [Image0], [t].[Information], [t].[LastName], [t].[SocialMedia]

    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t0]

    FROM [Episodes] AS [e]
    LEFT JOIN [Likes] AS [l] ON [e].[Id] = [l].[EpisodeId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[CreatedDate], [e0].[EpisodeId], [e0].[GuestId], [g].[Id] AS [Id0], [g].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [g].[FirstName], [g].[Image], [g].[Information], [g].[LastName], [g].[SocialMedia]

    ) AS [t2] ON [e].[Id] = [t2].[EpisodeId]
) AS [t1] ON [t0].[Id] = [t1].[PodcastId]

FROM [Podcasts] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [PodcastCategories] AS [p0] ON [p].[PodcastCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [TeamMembers] AS [t] ON [p].[TeamMemberId] = [t].[Id]

INNER JOIN [PodcastCategories] AS [p0] ON [p].[PodcastCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [TeamMembers] AS [t] ON [p].[TeamMemberId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e].[Id], [e].[Audio], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Description], [e].[Image], [e].[PodcastId], [e].[Title], [l].[Id] AS [Id0], [l].[AppUserId], [l].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [l].[EpisodeId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id1], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[EpisodeId] AS [EpisodeId0], [t1].[GuestId], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[FirstName], [t1].[Image] AS [Image0], [t1].[Information], [t1].[LastName], [t1].[SocialMedia]
    FROM [Episodes] AS [e]
    LEFT JOIN [Likes] AS [l] ON [e].[Id] = [l].[EpisodeId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[CreatedDate], [e0].[EpisodeId], [e0].[GuestId], [g].[Id] AS [Id0], [g].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [g].[FirstName], [g].[Image], [g].[Information], [g].[LastName], [g].[SocialMedia]
        FROM [EpisodeGuests] AS [e0]
        INNER JOIN [Guests] AS [g] ON [e0].[GuestId] = [g].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [e].[Id] = [t1].[EpisodeId]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[PodcastId]
ORDER BY [p].[CreatedDate] DESC, [p].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1]

SELECT [e].[Id], [e].[Audio], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Description], [e].[Image], [e].[PodcastId], [e].[Title], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Image], [p].[PodcastCategoryId], [p].[TeamMemberId], [p].[Title], [l].[Id], [l].[AppUserId], [l].[CreatedDate], [l].[EpisodeId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[EpisodeId], [t].[GuestId], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[FirstName], [t].[Image], [t].[Information], [t].[LastName], [t].[SocialMedia]
FROM [Episodes] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [Podcasts] AS [p] ON [e].[PodcastId] = [p].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Likes] AS [l] ON [e].[Id] = [l].[EpisodeId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[CreatedDate], [e0].[EpisodeId], [e0].[GuestId], [g].[Id] AS [Id0], [g].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [g].[FirstName], [g].[Image], [g].[Information], [g].[LastName], [g].[SocialMedia]
    FROM [EpisodeGuests] AS [e0]
    INNER JOIN [Guests] AS [g] ON [e0].[GuestId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [e].[Id] = [t].[EpisodeId]
ORDER BY [e].[CreatedDate] DESC, [e].[Id], [p].[Id], [l].[Id], [t].[Id]
